Q. how to add comments on css?
ans- comments can be added by following ways-
    1. sngle line comment //
    2. multi line comment /*     */
----------------------------------------------------------------------

Q. Why do we use pseudo-class?

ans. psedu class specify the special state of selected element.
        example- p:hover{
                    color : red;
                }
------------------------------------------------------------------------
Q. How is specificity applied?
ans- supoose two or more css is applied to an element. Then the selector which have higher specificity value
    its style will be applied to the element.
    example p{
            color : red;
            }
            .test_class p{
            color : green;
            }

            <p class="test_class">hello world</p>
        so in this example text color will be green because class selector has higher priority.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Q. What method allows an element to be moved from its current position?
ans- transform allow an element to be moved from its position. It rotate the
    element clockwise from its current position.


